Package: rctbayespower
Title: Bayesian Power Analysis for Randomized Controlled Trials
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Description: Provides tools to conduct Bayesian power analyses for randomized controlled trials (RCTs) using 'brms' and 'Stan'.
